  <num>1-1162.08</num>
  <heading>Quorum; delegation.</heading>
  <para>
    <num>(a)</num>
    <text>Two members of the Ethics Board shall constitute a quorum for the transaction of business.</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(b)</num>
    <text>The Ethics Board may delegate to an individual member or to the Director of Government Ethics its power to investigate or hold a hearing.</text>
  </para>
